- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possible category as the paper discusses risks associated with a proposed upgrade to the MCAS algorithm. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper touches on the role of human factors in the MCAS incidents. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the MCAS algorithm is a form of AI and the paper discusses potential flaws in its design.
